# Architecture

Feature-based structure under `src/features/`:
collection, deckbuilder, wishlist, market, pricing, trade, catalog, import, auth, dashboard

Shared: `src/components/shared/`, `src/hooks/`, `src/services/`, `src/types/`, `src/utils/`

## Before writing code
1. Analyze requirements
2. Suggest architecture
3. Explain state management (React Query = server, Zustand = UI)
4. Explain database changes
5. Explain reusable components
6. Then generate code

Strict TypeScript — no `any`. Small functions, maximum readability, no deeply nested logic.
